info.name: Spin 5
info.attribution:
Gameplay:

 Each Turn:
  - Place a piece anywhere
  - Rotate any square

 Winning:
  - Get 5 in a row (Diagonals Count)

 Ties:
  - Multiple players get 5 in a row simultaneously
  - Run out of space on the board 

The game layout, assets, and library image were created by https://www.reddit.com/user/Casbuild, https://www.reddit.com/user/RaphaelAlvez and https://www.reddit.com/user/96LawDawg and are released to the public domain by CC0.
info.description: Place marble into a space on four connected and rotating 3x3 grids. Connect five marbles in a row to win.
